            Fraser, a vibrant and contemporary hotel designed for the modern
            traveler. This stylish haven offers a unique blend of comfort and
            convenience, with a focus on social interaction and personalized
            service. Discover spacious and well-appointed studios and
            apartments, each featuring a modern kitchenette and a host of
            thoughtful amenities. Enjoy the vibrant social spaces, including a
